data.description: Built by custom local builder less than 2 years ago, still like new, but better! NO HOA FEES! Open concept floor plan with nearly all living space on one floor - Primary suite w/luxury bath, 2 more bedrooms, additional full & half bath down, 1 bedroom and half bath above the garage. Primary features a spacious walk-in closet and is King-size accommodating. Real Hardwood floors throughout the first floor, ceramic tile in all bathrooms and carpet in the bedrooms. Gourmet kitchen with island for prepping, eating or just gathering, with room for 4 bar stools. Stainless steel full appliance package, upgrade cabinets and a pantry as well. The living/dining area has lots of natural light, a cozy gas fireplace and a sliding door for access to your back deck and fully fenced yard. Full size utility room, one car attached garage! Room over the garage can be used as a bedroom, office, media room or play area. Easy access to huge attic storage space. Available for quick closing!
